sehold or business sharing a single Service Line count as **one** subscriber.\n  * *Example 2:* A single user or business with both a Residential Service Line and a separate Roam Service Line counts as **two** Starlink Subscribers. \n\nBecause of this definition, the company notes that the actual number of individual end-users accessing the network is likely "meaningfully higher" than the reported 10.3 million Starlink Subscribers.',
